General.Name: Puuilo Oyj
General.Description: Puuilo Oyj operates a discount retail store chain in Finland. It offers products in the categories of building, tools, HVAC and electric supplies, pet food and supplies, car accessories, groceries, household products, garden supplies, free-time and other products, and services. The company was founded in 1982 and is headquartered in Vantaa, Finland. Puuilo Oyj is a subsidiary of Puuilo Invest Holding AB.
